    <li class="publication  article">
  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Elucidating the synergistic mechanism of nickel-molybdenum electrocatalysts for the hydrogen evolution reaction</span>
  <i>MRS COMMUNICATIONS</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Mckay, I. S., Schwalbe, J. A., Goodman, E. D., Willis, J. J., Majumdar, A., Cargnello, M.</span>

<span class="details">
   <span class="year">2016</span>; <span class="volume">6 (3)</span><span class="pages">: 241-246</span>
</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
      <p class="doi">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://dx.doi.org/10.1557/mrc.2016.27">DOI 10.1557/mrc.2016.27</a></span>
  </p>
  <p class="wos">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://ws.isiknowledge.com/cps/openurl/service?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:ut/000389137400013">Web of Science ID 000389137400013</a></span>
