  <span>Nanoscale thermal transport</span>
  <i>JOURNAL OF APPLIED PHYSICS</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Cahill, D. G., FORD, W. K., Goodson, K. E., Mahan, G. D., Majumdar, A., Maris, H. J., Merlin, R., Phillpot, S. R.</span>

<span class="details">
   <span class="year">2003</span>; <span class="volume">93 (2)</span><span class="pages">: 793-818</span>
</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
      <p class="doi">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://dx.doi.org/10.1063/1.1524305">DOI 10.1063/1.1524305</a></span>
  </p>
  <p class="wos">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://ws.isiknowledge.com/cps/openurl/service?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:ut/000180134200001">Web of Science ID 000180134200001</a></span>
