    <li class="publication featured article">
  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Thermometry and thermal transport in micro/nanoscale solid-state devices and structures</span>
  <i>JOURNAL OF HEAT TRANSFER-TRANSACTIONS OF THE ASME</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Cahill, D. G., Goodson, K. E., Majumdar, A.</span>

<span class="details">
   <span class="year">2002</span>; <span class="volume">124 (2)</span><span class="pages">: 223-241</span>
</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
      <p class="doi">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://dx.doi.org/10.1115/1.1454111">DOI 10.1115/1.1454111</a></span>
  </p>
  <p class="wos">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://ws.isiknowledge.com/cps/openurl/service?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:ut/000175917200002">Web of Science ID 000175917200002</a></span>
  </p>
      
